<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mindfighter Hub | Adventures of the Mind</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --neon-blue: #00f2ff;
            --deep-space: #0a0a12;
            --manga-white: #f5f5f5;
        }
        body {
            background-color: var(--deep-space);
            color: var(--manga-white);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 10, 18, 0.8), rgba(10, 10, 18, 0.8)), 
                        url('https://path-to-your-anime-art.jpg') center/cover;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--neon-blue);
        }
        .biometric-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 1px, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 1px, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 2px);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .btn-access {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--neon-blue);
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-access:hover {
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            color: var(--deep-space);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--neon-blue);
        }
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 50px;
            background: #11111d;
        }
        .card {
            border: 1px solid #333;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--neon-blue);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="biometric-overlay"></div>

<section class="hero">
    <h1>ADVENTURES OF THE MIND</h1>
    <p>THE THREADS OF HSA | MINDFIGHTER CORE V.1.0</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <button class="btn-access" onclick="alert('Initializing Biometric Scan...')">Initialize Entry</button>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="feature-grid">
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Biometric NFT Security</h3>
        <p>Your access is tied to a unique biological signature, ensuring secure ownership of the Mindfighter Beginnings ecosystem.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Kaleidoscope HUD</h3>
        <p>Experience the world through the Codex lens with geometric line overlays and technical data visualization.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Manga Integration</h3>
        <p>Custom anime-style watermarks and character overlays bridge the gap between digital literature and visual media.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #555;">
        OFFICIAL PRODUCT OF MINDFIGHTER HUB | POWERED BY B.A.N.G MEDIA
    </p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
